->[/b][/color] It's my personal presets, i'm not modder. If you like, endorse :D

[b]How to install:[/b]

[b]1)[/b] Go to [url=http://enbdev.com/mod_tesskyrim_v0112.htm]http://enbdev.com/mod_tesskyrim_v0112.htm[/url] , download and extract only "d3d9.dll"
   from "Wrapper" folder to your Skyrim main folder.

[b]2)[/b] Copy all files from "Main Files" folder to your Skyrim main folder.

[b]3)[/b] You're free to edit this preset as you wish.

[b]4)[/b] [color=#6aa84f](Optional)[/color] If you want, use my Skyrim INI's for performance and quality.
     Open the SkyrimPrefs.ini and edit this line: sD3DDevice="Your Device Name Here"

[b]5)[/b] Enjoy!
